reviewText: The price I paid for three Christmas movies was great.  Christmas in Boston was very romantic.  This was my favorite movie.  Santa Baby 2 was ok but I liked the original one better.  Snowglobe was cute.  It was different to see your life differently through your own eyes.
Title: Santa Baby 2: Christmas Maybe / Christmas in Boston / Snowglobe

reviewText: I have a Christmas video collection very similar to this, except the titles are "Santa's Making Babies"/"Christmas Orgy in Boston" and "Look at my Huge Snowglobes". My buddy Sgt "old as dirt" Mikey from Germany recommended them to me, as he is a Christmas movie freak. I have a feeling ol Sgt Mikey is yanking our chain with his review---we all know what he's really watching down in the that man cave amidst his Zagnut bars, Diet Rite colas and his lotions......
summary: Huh....I have a collection very similar to this......
Title: Santa Baby 2: Christmas Maybe / Christmas in Boston / Snowglobe

reviewText: I bought this as a Christmas gift for my sister who is in love with everything Christmas and if it were up to her, it would be Christmas every freaking day. She loved it. And it's a great price for all three.
summary: Bought this as  a Christmas gift.
Title: Santa Baby 2: Christmas Maybe / Christmas in Boston / Snowglobe

reviewText: I bought these for our Christmas enjoymen and we really have enjoyed them.  It was everything I expected at a price I could afford and the service was great  I have really enjoyed them. Thank you
